                  <div align="left"> 
                    <img src="/mbimages/eaglerequired.jpg" align="right"><img src="/mbimages/eaglerequired.jpg" align="right"><img src="/mbimagespng/boating.png" align="right" vspace="5" hspace="5"><span class="maintext">

<h1>Boating</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Before doing the other requirements, swim 100 yards using any stroke, then rest by floating as still as you can for one minute.<p>

<li>Show that you know safety rules for boating or sailing.<p>

<li>Secure a permit to operate a motorboat if needed. Explain the laws affecting pleasure boating in your area.<p>

<li>Show that before going in a boat, you know the features or hazards of the body of water to be cruised.<p>

<li>Explain the rules of the sea lanes. Describe aids to navigation used where you cruised.<p>

<li>Examine the condition, and demonstrate the proper use of the following safety gears.
<ol type=a>
<li>Lifesaving device for each person on board
<li>Fire extinguisher
<li>Oars of paddles
<li>Light
<li>Tool kit
<li>Extra shear pin and spark plugs
<li>Horn, whistle, or other sound signals
<li>Compass
<li>Anchor and line
<li>Safety chain (for outboard motor)
<li>First aid kit
<li>Bilge pump or similar device that can be used for bailing.</ol></ol>


			
</span><p><div class="fb-comments" data-href="http://www.mbcenter.org/htm/meritbadges.php?mb=boating" data-width="540" data-numposts="10"></div>                  <p>&nbsp;</p></div>
